name: Database user
description: JIRA Database user name with SELECT grant. Must have INSERT/DELETE/DELETE grants for import tools

name: User name
description: JIRA user name able to perform index. Required only for import tools

name: Password
description: JIRA password of user able to perform index

name: User name
description: User name able to create, update and execute a job

name: User name
description: User name able to manage SonarQube

name: Password
description: User password able to manage SonarQube

name: Parent Group
description: Parent group name of this new group. Useful to create a sub group like 'customer', 'test',...

name: UID Pattern
description: Pattern determining the login can be processed by the node

name: User
description: DN of administrative user that can fetch the repository

name: Base DN
description: Base DN where people, groups and companies are located

name: People DN
description: DN of location of any user that can login

name: People Internal DN
description: DN of location of people considered as internal. May be the same than people

name: Groups DN
description: DN of location of any groups

name: Quarantine DN
description: DN of location where isolated users are moved to

name: UID attribute
description: LDAP schema attribute name of login

name: Local identifier attribute
description: LDAP schema attribute name of internal id of login. May not be unique.

name: Locked Attribute
description: LDAP schema attribute holding the locked state of a user.

name: Locked value
description: Value used as flog for a locked user inside the locked attribute

name: Company pattern
description: Pattern capturing the company from the DN of the user. May be a row string for constant.

name: People Object Class
description: Object Class of people : organizationalPerson, inetOrgPerson

name: User name
description: Confluence user name able to perform index and create spaces

name: Password
description: Confluence password of user able to perform index and create spaces

name: User name
description: Fortify user name at least able to query the projects

name: Password
description: Fortify password of user able to perform index

name: User name
description: vCloud user name, case is sensitive. Will encoded with the organization to build the authentication token

name: Organization
description: vCloud organization. It will encoded with the user to build the authentication token

name: User name
description: User able to create and fetch repositories

name: Has index
description: Node as an index listing repositories

name: User name
description: User able to create and fetch repositories

name: Has index
description: Node as an index listing repositories

name: User name
description: User able to create and fetch projects

name: User name
description: User able to create and fetch shared directories
